  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You have 12 weeks to turn the recruits into soldiers!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698350/extras/093bf4848d470cdd5cd8f45cadffb3fb.poster.avif?t=1762761599\" width=600 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698350/extras/093bf4848d470cdd5cd8f45cadffb3fb.webm?t=1762761599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698350/extras/093bf4848d470cdd5cd8f45cadffb3fb.mp4?t=1762761599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Develop your training schedule. If their Stamina runs out or if their Stress becomes too much, they may fail their training... or worse. More effective advanced training can be unlocked by expending Prestige Points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698350/extras/c445196538b75d4bb778fc2e777e5cdb.poster.avif?t=1762761599\" width=600 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698350/extras/c445196538b75d4bb778fc2e777e5cdb.webm?t=1762761599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698350/extras/c445196538b75d4bb778fc2e777e5cdb.mp4?t=1762761599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Improve your soldiers and earn more Prestige Points when they graduate. Qualify them as riflemen divers, snipers, or paratroopers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698350/extras/45010975bc7ec06ec14f326fed0b595f.poster.avif?t=1762761599\" width=600 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698350/extras/45010975bc7ec06ec14f326fed0b595f.webm?t=1762761599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698350/extras/45010975bc7ec06ec14f326fed0b595f.mp4?t=1762761599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Do you have the right recruit to win a 100m sprint? Or to challenge a naval academy in a swimming competition? What about the marksmanship challenge? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698350/extras/66bb2a145a434fc7370383a5ed28ecb7.poster.avif?t=1762761599\" width=600 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698350/extras/66bb2a145a434fc7370383a5ed28ecb7.webm?t=1762761599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698350/extras/66bb2a145a434fc7370383a5ed28ecb7.mp4?t=1762761599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Check your men's skill in mission. Make choices based on the encounters you find. Have you based your training program on agility and close-combat? Then better a sneak approach...</p>",
